{"tid":1548150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大專學界代表團IAD出訪澳洲","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:18:47.000Z","uid":139698,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb36007fad55e83ac988340a9693c1dcf8e8bcc6","tid":1548150,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIAD成員到達墨爾本後，接受了澳洲最大廣播公司ABC News 和 SBS News 的電視台丶電台和紙媒專訪，稍後會在全國播出。<br />\n<br />\n訪談中，大專學界代表團提出：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府需即時回應民間五大需求</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲政府需要保障香港在澳留學生的安全</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲政府應擱置與香港政府簽訂《澳洲-香港自由貿易協定》</span><br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲政府應立法通過Global Magnitsky Act 制裁損害香港自治的官員</span><br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲政府應對香港實施人道援助<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzkAreN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzkAreN.jpg&h=d63de1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會見傳媒只是第一步，未來數天，代表團將約見澳洲不同政黨和學生組織，表達我們的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支持澳洲政府給予保護簽證居澳港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au:v12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fprime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia%3Futm_content%3Dbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12%26recruited_by_id%3Df7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612%26recruiter%3D889993192%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=85991cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au:v12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition</a>"},{"pid":"684a29a2a2b7da8f8f53f1e45014e1a372a8c829","tid":1548150,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91cb7f02f074158f50d1c7aefef94ff9b3ea5fd9","tid":1548150,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b9f056e67ea1d2b76e051bd0f707d88c98742a9","tid":1548150,"uid":137360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a495f3934d1f1b2598cb186a81ae622295adaa6","tid":1548150,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cc77c13ff48f4db307542157c93587bf6673057","tid":1548150,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69dcb693d478887c7b51a45f25fc0e584e28dc35","tid":1548150,"uid":44758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:43:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以講埋幾時播出，如果報紙都有想買番份留起佢<br />\n<br />\n利申： 澳洲巴打"},{"pid":"b035cb51466ea759ffc04e3c98b79bc1a8b03dc8","tid":1548150,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0be272e6e044c7a72edb8d2bedf14a91362898c","tid":1548150,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69dcb693d478887c7b51a45f25fc0e584e28dc35","tid":1548150,"uid":44758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:43:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以講埋幾時播出，如果報紙都有想買番份留起佢<br />\n<br />\n利申： 澳洲巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"go to their Facebook page, check it out.<br />\n<br />\n海外港人支援陣線<br />\n<br />\n從6月9日，「反送中」運動開始，1百萬人、2百萬人+1上街後，港共仍堅持與港人為敵，因而上演了621的血腥鎮壓及開始了這場運動中的政治檢控，至今被政治迫害的人數已超過1000人，當中更有不少被強姦、非禮、毆打、殘害及以酷刑對待，所以哪怕能撤回修例，但已不能回到當初，這些被殘害的，被犧牲的，誰能還他們一個公道？！<br />\n<br />\n然而各位也明白，共匪從不會解決問題，只會解決提出問題的人，因此香港的所有義士及一眾海外曾向這極權說不的人，更加會視為清算的首要目標。<br />\n有見及此，一些熱心人士於早前已向一些澳洲政黨求助，亦很感謝《一國黨》（One Nation）及《綠黨》（Greens）願意為拯救香港人發聲，我們這一群在澳無助的港人們，真的極需要各政黨們的支持，因而我們極歡迎澳洲的任何政黨為人權、良知、公義替我們發聲、站檯。<br />\n在未來我們會有一些行動，所以亦希望在澳港人能為拯救港人多走一步，因此希望各位有心人士填寫以下表格，登記成為義工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSetdnAdG-U0T-ipcw2Cn6q7oXKDB47YR6BZVCo927zLfvUOAg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSetdnAdG-U0T-ipcw2Cn6q7oXKDB47YR6BZVCo927zLfvUOAg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7d7d9a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSetdnAdG-U0T-ipcw2Cn6q7oXKDB47YR6BZVCo927zLfvUOAg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家簽署保護澳洲香港人的請願，讓海外的國際社會係依場運動上多加分力， 竭盡所能將議題推入國會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/rGSnfQFPX2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FrGSnfQFPX2&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=fc8e968d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/rGSnfQFPX2</a><br />\n<br />\n在此再次感激每位為自由、民主、人權、公義去付出血汗的義士們，We are Hongkonger &amp; we are not alone ！！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人～～加油💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻<br />\n一群在澳洲的香港素人"}]}